data.description:
Get $500 off first month rental price when signed by Jan 26 (to move in Feb 1). (Valid from 01/12/2024 till 01/26/2024)

In a friendly neighborhood home to young families, retirees, and young professionals. Convenient to park, splash pad, Gardendale urban trail system, and food and shopping (Target, Lowe's, Publix, TJ Maxx). Just a 15-20 minute drive to downtown/UAB, with minimal traffic. Home has spacious rooms, abundant natural light, and an open layout. Backyard is fenced with landscaping and a covered patio. Pets allowed.

Pictures coming soon. Pictures are also available on zillow.com listing of 1355 Woodridge Pl, Gardendale, AL 35071.

No smoking allowed. Only two pets allowed (dogs and cats only). Renter is responsible for all utilities (gas, trash, power, water, internet, etc.) and maintaining lawn to HOA standards (lawn equipment is provided). 

12 month lease minimum. $1,000 security deposit required for any damage sustained to the property during the lease term. If lease broken early, three months of rent will be due.
